London Page 23
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Tight control of overheads and production costs enabled Shani Group to
produce a pre-tax profit of Pounds 770,000 for the half year to January 31
1992, compared with Pounds 764,000.
This USM-traded maker of women's and children's clothes saw its margins
