Industries, Germany; Wilhelm Wilhelmsen, Wilhelm Wilhelmsen, Norway; Lynton
R Wilson, BCE Inc, Canada; Rona Yircali, Yapi Kredi Bank and Mortas Mining
Co, Turkey.
This letter has also been sent to heads of state and governments of major
trading nations
