<DATELINE>
   BRUSSELS
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
The European Commission is imposing provisional anti-dumping duties on
imports of alloy engineering steel billets from Brazil and Turkey, Reuter
reports from Brussels. The duties, equal to 16 per cent on imports from
Turkey and 15 per cent on Brazilian steel, were imposed after an
investigation following a complaint from the EC steel industry.
